"{\"uid\": \"nbcnewyork.com-paris-2024-summer-olympics-ugandan-sprinter-minions-spongebob-socks-paris-olympics-5684341\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Tarsis Gracious Orogot of Team Uganda competes in the Men's 200m Semi-Final on day twelve of the Olympic Games Paris 2024 at Stade de France on August 07, 2024 in Paris, France.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 177, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 163, \"end\": 168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999331857929, \"rank\": 6.681424423828582e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 170, \"end\": 176, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8315283750411412, \"rank\": 0.19955532220695735, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic fans can not wait to see what Tarsis Orogot wears next after he sported colorful socks in the first 200m race and at the semifinal.\", \"from\": 179, \"to\": 318, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Orogot, a student athlete on the University of Alabama's track & field team, caught spectators' eyes on Monday during the second heat of the hotly contested race with his pair of SpongeBob Squarepants socks.\", \"from\": 320, \"to\": 527, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 499, \"end\": 520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SpongeBob_SquarePants\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"SpongeBob Squarepants\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SpongeBob_SquarePants\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SpongeBob_SquarePants\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The bright yellow Nickelodeon character was with him as he sprinted and qualified for the semifinal.\", \"from\": 528, \"to\": 628, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 546, \"end\": 557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nickelodeon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.904446843739411e-28, \"text\": \"Nickelodeon\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nickelodeon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nickelodeon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Spongebob socks so you know he's ready \\u203c\\ufe0fTarsis Orogot speeds into the 200m semifinal.#ParisOlympics\\ud83d\\udcfa NBC & Peacockpic.twitter.com/xWFqTQ6WIy  Watch NBC 4 free wherever you are  At the men's 200m semifinal on Wednesday, the 21-year-old did not disappoint and showed up to the track with a pair of the Minions socks.\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 945, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 780, \"end\": 783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.899543289064531, \"rank\": 0.0704501097246183, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The creatures from well-loved animated films even had their goggles and arms sticking out from the socks.\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 1051, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Those little arms were swinging as Orogot raced down the track.\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Unfortunately, his time of 20.64 seconds was not enough to send him to the final.\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1198, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Perhaps he will still show up in another pair of fun socks to watch the competition.\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1284, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Whaaaaat!?\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1296, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Uganda's Orogothas Minion socks on for this 200M semifinal.\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1356, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1298, \"end\": 1304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"score\": 0.9938405454943291, \"rank\": 0.003065300688226406, \"text\": \"Uganda\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like actual little goggles.#Paris2024#Olympicspic.twitter.com/9iijKVehMY  The 2024 Paris Olympics is not the first time Orogot is seen with his signature socks.\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1517, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In another race, he wore the SpongeBob sock before on one side, and Patrick Star on the other.\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1612, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1587, \"end\": 1594, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patrick_Star\", \"score\": 0.9999999495773876, \"rank\": 5.04226496567254e-08, \"text\": \"Patrick\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patrick_Star\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patrick_Star\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On hisInstagram, there are photos and videos of him wearing Iron Man socks, Sonic the Hedgehog socks and even Cookie Monster socks.\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1744, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1674, \"end\": 1682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iron_Man\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.396706434980409e-17, \"text\": \"Iron Man\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iron_Man\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iron_Man\"}, {\"begin\": 1700, \"end\": 1708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hedgehog\", \"score\": 0.9999994544231537, \"rank\": 3.895602473666539e-07, \"text\": \"Hedgehog\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hedgehog\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hedgehog\"}, {\"begin\": 1724, \"end\": 1738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cookie_Monster\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cookie Monster\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cookie_Monster\", \"dbpedia\": \"http:/